r much discussion with charterers and pilots, we agreed to bring her in on high tide a day after arrival with additional pilots and tugs. Chevron has confirmed they will cover these additional costs. \n-\tA small amount of waiting time was incurred at load and discharge, allowing us to bill $56k demurrage. (2.25 days @ $25kpd). Some time was split 50/50 due to lightning delays at discharge.\n-\tThere was a discrepancy of 22.6mt for VLSFO delivered at Bolivar"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}